info.author: Ryan Simpson
info.name: tentacletk
info.summary: Tentacle is a marking menu style UI and toolkit derived from a QStackedWidget and constructed using the uitk backend. It aims to bring a similar UI experience across multiple dcc modeling applications that support the PySide2 GUI framework.
